source:
TEXT_DUNGEONDAIMYOYASHIKI_00000_KAGEYAMA_000_000You've done well to make it this far, but I'm afraid
your journey ends here. Come, Yojimbo! We have visitors!
target:
TEXT_DUNGEONDAIMYOYASHIKI_00000_KAGEYAMA_000_000よ～くぞ ここまで やって来たなぁ～！
じゃが この「用心棒」には かなうま～い！！

source:
TEXT_DUNGEONDAIMYOYASHIKI_00000_YOJIMBO_000_100Your coffers appear empty, Kageyama.
If you cannot pay my price, then I am finished here.
target:
TEXT_DUNGEONDAIMYOYASHIKI_00000_YOJIMBO_000_100カゲヤマも もはや すかんぴん……
これ以上 戦う義理もなし…… しからば 御免……！
